title: 2BR apt | Wood-style flooring | Modern kitchen | Prime Auburn location
posting_body: ['Welcome Home To Sherwood Gardens!', 'Sherwood Gardens is a beautiful and friendly park-like apartment community that offers comfortable living at affordable prices.', 'The beautiful Sherwood Gardens grounds include a playground, pool and picnic area.', 'Residents can choose from one and two bedroom apartment layouts, completed with amenities such as all-electric kitchen, ceiling fans, walk-in closets, kitchen pantry, and more!', 'Small cats and dogs are welcome for an additional deposit - restrictions apply.', 'This apartment features:', 'NEW!', 'stainless-steel appliances', 'Plenty of natural light', 'Open concept living room', 'Fully-equipped kitchen with pantry', 'Generous closets', 'Parking space included', '12 month lease available', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'Come Visit us!', 'Sherwood Gardens', '2901 Auburn Way S', 'Auburn, WA 98092', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Monday – Friday 9:00am – 6:00pm', 'Saturday 10:00am – 5:00pm', 'Closed on Sunday', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.']
